N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 177.6 - Conflicts with law and regulation; collective bargaining rights not diminished

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part shall not be construed to
diminish or waive any rights or obligations of any nurse or health care
provider pursuant to any other law, regulation, or collective bargaining
agreement. Notes
